mpi-defaults (0.6) unstable; urgency=low

  * Set Standards-Version to 3.8.2. No changes needed.
  * Added lpia to list of supported architectures, defaulting to
    Open MPI. Thanks to Steven Susbauer! (Closes: #532643)

